@* THE CONTROL for register C4: the SAME component as ExplicitComponentBase, with NO @inherits line at
   all. Its emitted module must be BYTE-IDENTICAL to ExplicitComponentBase's -- which is the proof that
   `@inherits ComponentBase` is a no-op, exactly as Razor's own codegen treats it. *@

<div id="wrap"><span id="out">@currentCount</span><button id="inc" @onclick="Increment">inc</button></div>

@code {
    int currentCount = 5;
    void Increment() { currentCount++; }
}
